(133, 1, '2021-12-15 11:48:19', '2021-12-15 10:48:19', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are three close friends who live in New York and share the passion for Fashion Books. We founded this Fashion eBook Store to share our passion with people world wide.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Oxford University anthropologist Robin Dunbar has studied human relationships in societies from the Stone Age to Facebook. According  to Dunbar healthy people maintain between three to five close friends who can be relied upon in times of trouble. If your own friend count (just like ours) falls within that range, and  you share the passion for fashion books, you\'re doing fine.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2021-12-15 13:19:48', '2021-12-15 12:19:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8000/?page_id=133', 0, 'page', '', 0),
